description: Fun, fresh and filling. This Mexican-style macaroni salad with black beans and tomato is bursting with colour and flavour. Try this recipe for an easy dinner or side.
keywords: Pasta salad,Pescatarian,Low saturated fat,Seafood free,Low salt,Tree nut free,Low sugar,Sesame free,Halal,High protein,High fibre,Soy free,Vegetarian,Vegan,Quick & easy lunch,Tomato,Low fat,Peanut free
name: Mexican-Style Macaroni Salad Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 0.5 bunch continental parsley, leaves picked, roughly chopped

recipeInstructions.text: Heat pasta according to packet instructions. Transfer to a large bowl and stir to separate pasta.
Add beans, corn, tomato and parsley to pasta. Squeeze over half the lime and drizzle with oil. Toss to combine. Season.
Top pasta salad with extra parsley and serve with remaining lime wedges.
